data.description:
Welcome to your new family haven! This charming residence on Lucustberry Drive offers the perfect blend of comfort and space. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there's ample room for everyone. The heart of the home features a beautiful kitchen, flowing seamlessly into the dining and living areas - ideal for entertaining or simply spending quality time together.

But that's not all. Imagine having an additional second living area that can be tailored to your needs - a playroom, a home office, or a cozy reading nook, the choice is yours. The possibilities are endless. Step outside to a well-maintained yard, ready for outdoor activities or relaxation.

Don't miss the chance to make this house your family's new home sweet home!
